author: aconway
msg: DISPATCH-116: Managment clients and tests use anonymous@ to trigger SASL connection by proton.
Recent changes in proton mean that by default it does no SASL handshake on connection.
Dispatch requires SASL, using "anonymous@" in the connection URL for proton triggers

author: aconway
msg: NO-JIRA: Fixed error output of qdrouterd in non-daemon mode, fixed bug in qd_error_errno.
In non-daemon mode qdrouterd start-up errors were being lost.
Also fixed a bug in qd_error_errno, the errno message was not being printed.
